{
  "Let's start off with the most basic example, alerting <span class=\"sparkle_wrapper__cL2jQ\"><span class=\"sparkle_sparkle_wrapper__Izdcu\" style=\"top:35%;left:2%\"><svg class=\"sparkle_sparkle_svg__WdZ3Y\" fill=\"none\" height=\"19\" viewbox=\"0 0 68 68\" width=\"19\"><path d=\"M 48 5 L 51 27 L 74 30 L 51 33 L 48 56 L 44 33 L 23 30 L 44 27 Z\" fill=\"var(--yellow)\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"sparkle_sparkle_wrapper__Izdcu\" style=\"top:89%;left:5%\"><svg class=\"sparkle_sparkle_svg__WdZ3Y\" fill=\"none\" height=\"15\" viewbox=\"0 0 68 68\" width=\"15\"><path d=\"M 48 5 L 51 27 L 74 30 L 51 33 L 48 56 L 44 33 L 23 30 L 44 27 Z\" fill=\"var(--yellow)\"></path></svg></span><strong class=\"sparkle_child_wrapper__bem0y\">OUCH</strong></span> whenever a user clicks on a button.": "我们先从最基础的例子开始 —— 当用户点击按钮时弹出 <span class=\"sparkle_wrapper__cL2jQ\"><span class=\"sparkle_sparkle_wrapper__Izdcu\" style=\"top:35%;left:2%\"><svg class=\"sparkle_sparkle_svg__WdZ3Y\" fill=\"none\" height=\"19\" viewbox=\"0 0 68 68\" width=\"19\"><path d=\"M 48 5 L 51 27 L 74 30 L 51 33 L 48 56 L 44 33 L 23 30 L 44 27 Z\" fill=\"var(--yellow)\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"sparkle_sparkle_wrapper__Izdcu\" style=\"top:89%;left:5%\"><svg class=\"sparkle_sparkle_svg__WdZ3Y\" fill=\"none\" height=\"15\" viewbox=\"0 0 68 68\" width=\"15\"><path d=\"M 48 5 L 51 27 L 74 30 L 51 33 L 48 56 L 44 33 L 23 30 L 44 27 Z\" fill=\"var(--yellow)\"></path></svg></span><strong class=\"sparkle_child_wrapper__bem0y\">OUCH</strong></span>。",
  "Next, you'll notice that we're passing our event handler as a <em metastring=\"\">reference</em> to <code>onClick</code>, not as an <em metastring=\"\">invocation</em>. Note the difference between these two <code>onClick</code> props.": "其次，注意我们是把事件处理函数作为<em metastring=\"\">引用</em>传给 <code>onClick</code>，而不是作为<em metastring=\"\">调用</em>。留意这两种 <code>onClick</code> prop 的区别。",
  "If we pass <code>onClick</code> an <em metastring=\"\">invocation</em>, à la <code>handleClick()</code>, as soon as the JavaScript engine encounters the invocation, it will invoke the function and pass the return value to <code>onClick</code>. This is obviously not what we want.": "如果我们给 <code>onClick</code> 传的是<em metastring=\"\">调用</em>形式（比如 <code>handleClick()</code>），那 JavaScript 引擎一碰到这个调用就会立刻执行函数，并把返回值传给 <code>onClick</code>。显然这不是我们想要的。",
  "Instead, we want to pass <code>onClick</code> a <em metastring=\"\">reference</em> to the function, so that it can invoke the function when the event occurs.": "我们真正想做的是把函数的<em metastring=\"\">引用</em>传给 <code>onClick</code>，这样它才能在事件发生时自己去调用函数。",
  "Next, you'll notice that we created our event handler <em metastring=\"\">inside</em> the component, not outside of it. This is also a common pattern, but it may feel unintuitive at first. Can you think of why we do this?": "另一个细节是，我们把事件处理函数写在了 component <em metastring=\"\">内部</em>，而不是外部。这也是常见写法，但乍看可能不太直观。你能想到原因吗？",
  "We no longer have access to <code>message</code> via scope. Instead, we have to pass it as an argument to <code>handleClick</code>, which forces us to create <em metastring=\"\">another</em> function that we pass to <code>onClick</code>. This indirection is unnecessary and is a good indication that we should move <code>handleClick</code> back inside of our component so we can take advantage of lexical scoping.": "我们不再能通过作用域直接拿到 <code>message</code>，只能把它作为参数传给 <code>handleClick</code>，这就逼得我们必须再多写<em metastring=\"\">一个</em>函数再传给 <code>onClick</code>。这种多一层间接的写法完全没必要，也明确说明了我们应该把 <code>handleClick</code> 搬回 component 内部，好利用词法作用域。",
  "So at this point you know how to add a click handler to a <code>button</code> (which is <span class=\"font-black tracking-wider\" style=\"color:var(--blue)\">cool</span>), but let's look at a scenario that isn't straight out of a generic React tutorial.": "至此你已经知道如何给 <code>button</code> 加点击处理函数了（<span class=\"font-black tracking-wider\" style=\"color:var(--blue)\">不错</span>），下面来看一个不那么像通用 React 教程的场景。",
  "Now let's work on our event handler that we'll pass as an <button aria-controls=\"radix-:rau:\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" class=\"Popover_children__8p5Di\" data-state=\"closed\" type=\"button\"><span><code>onCopy</code></span> <svg class=\"fill-brand-purple dark:fill-brand-yellow w-2 h-2 b-2 mx-0.5 mb-4\" enable-background=\"new 0 0 455 455\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 455 455\" x=\"0\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" y=\"0\"><path d=\"M347.49 227L454.5 165.212 394.508 61.288 287.5 123.077 287.5 0 167.5 0 167.5 123.077 60.492 61.288 0.499 165.212 107.51 227 0.5 288.788 60.492 392.712 167.5 330.923 167.5 455 287.5 455 287.5 330.923 394.508 392.712 454.501 288.788z\"></path></svg></button> prop to each of our three emojis.": "现在来写事件处理函数，我们要把它作为 <button aria-controls=\"radix-:rau:\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" class=\"Popover_children__8p5Di\" data-state=\"closed\" type=\"button\"><span><code>onCopy</code></span> <svg class=\"fill-brand-purple dark:fill-brand-yellow w-2 h-2 b-2 mx-0.5 mb-4\" enable-background=\"new 0 0 455 455\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 455 455\" x=\"0\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" y=\"0\"><path d=\"M347.49 227L454.5 165.212 394.508 61.288 287.5 123.077 287.5 0 167.5 0 167.5 123.077 60.492 61.288 0.499 165.212 107.51 227 0.5 288.788 60.492 392.712 167.5 330.923 167.5 455 287.5 455 287.5 330.923 394.508 392.712 454.501 288.788z\"></path></svg></button> prop 传给这三个 emoji 中的每一个。",
  "This does bring up a new scenario though. We now need to know some specific information about the event that was triggered. Specifically, we need to know <em metastring=\"\">which</em> emoji was copied so we can see if it was the right one.": "不过这里出现了新的情况。我们现在需要知道所触发事件的一些具体信息 —— 具体来说，是<em metastring=\"\">哪一个</em> emoji 被复制了，这样才能判断是不是对的那个。",
  "<button aria-controls=\"radix-:rc7:\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-label=\"onGotPointerCapture\" class=\"Popover_children__8p5Di\" data-state=\"closed\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" type=\"button\"><span><p class=\"text-[16px] font-bold py-1\">onGotPointerCapture<span class=\"font-bold pr-2\">, </span></p></span> </button>": "<button aria-controls=\"radix-:rc7:\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-label=\"onGotPointerCapture\" class=\"Popover_children__8p5Di\" data-state=\"closed\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" type=\"button\"><span><p class=\"text-[16px] font-bold py-1\">onGotPointerCapture<span class=\"font-bold pr-2\">, </span></p></span> </button>",
